Need feedback on our 99designs logo design contest
text:
Hi everyone,

I'm currently hosting a logo design contest on 99designs for my Shopify app, Delm Delivery Date Estimator.

I would really appreciate if you could take a moment to check out the designs and give me some feedback via the poll on 99designs.

The poll link is: https://en.99designs.de/contests/poll/4bc1cad60f

And for context here's the app store listing: https://apps.shopify.com/delm

Thanks in advance!

PS: I understand the criticism aimed at 99designs, but participating in a design contest isn't just about winning prize money. Designers know what they're signing up for and can still benefit greatly from the experience. They have the chance to learn and improve their skills, and may even end up with a one-on-one client project as a result.
